        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/B_5iDPpjQkE" frameborder="0" allow="encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cn-layoutBlock__container">
      <div class="cn-layoutBlock__container__title">
        About Christy
      </div>
      <p>
        On a whim over a decade ago, Christy signed up for a weekend metalsmithing class as a creative outlet from her pre-med and psychology studies. As a little luck would have it, on that day she met both her love of working with metal and her now husband. After further pursuing her jewelry studies, she started her namesake business in 2013 and has enjoyed working with amazing clients in the San Francisco Bay Area and beyond.
      </p>
    </div>
